 Logic & Pseudocode


Logic Flow

Initialize System
Panel parameters 
Environmental conditions (sun position, ambient temp)
Simulate Time Progression
Update sun position (hour angle)
Compute irradiance and temperature
Calculate efficiency factors
Animate Results
Show panel, sun position, and efficiency metrics

Pseudocode

1. Set panel parameters
2. Initialize environment: G_max, T_ambient, dust_rate
3. For each timestep:
   a. Update sun position (hour angle)
   b. Compute irradiance G (solar noon = max)
   c. Calculate panel temperature T
   d. Compute angle factor f_angle
   e. Update dust accumulation
   f. Calculate efficiency Î·
4. Draw panel, sun, and efficiency graph
5. Repeat for animation
